{"tid":2318283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"卓悅大股東是「紫荊黨」創辦人","createTime":"2020-12-09T08:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T04:28:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c5a90243cb5e2c5f4ca9f04bf9a4e81410b6e3","tid":2318283,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:31:37.000Z","msg":"【卓悅欠租】卓悅欠租400萬遭清盤 現任主席是「紫荊黨」創辦人<br />\n<br />\n09 Dec 2020<br />\nDigital Editor<br />\n。。<br />\n卓悅創辦人葉俊亨夫婦於今年2月，將所持約的40.4%股權以約1.58億元轉讓給當時的第二大股東陳健文。<strong>陳健文從原本的約19.5%股權增至約59.9%，晉級成為公司大股東</strong>。另外，該公司於5月再度經歷一場人事變動，葉俊亨卸下主席與行政總裁一職，改為副主席，董事會主席則是由陳健文接任。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>陳健文除了身兼卓悅大股東身份，同時也是本地新政黨「紫荊黨」創辦人之一。</strong>據悉，該政黨於今年5月低調成立，旨在支持「一國兩制」，並改善中央與特區關係，計畫吸納25萬黨員。<br />\n<br />\nText by BusinessFocus Editorial<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.io/article/153338/%E5%8D%93%E6%82%85-%E6%B8%85%E7%9B%A4?fbclid=IwAR0wv_oGGC5brkw076DFFtqCb9dtJZVb8AaWJ0W2p16_V6DkhQ9aC9RFujQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2Farticle%2F153338%2F%25E5%258D%2593%25E6%2582%2585-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%259B%25A4%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0wv_oGGC5brkw076DFFtqCb9dtJZVb8AaWJ0W2p16_V6DkhQ9aC9RFujQ&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=01d740b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.io/article/153338/%E5%8D%93%E6%82%85-%E6%B8%85%E7%9B%A4?fbclid=IwAR0wv_oGGC5brkw076DFFtqCb9dtJZVb8AaWJ0W2p16_V6DkhQ9aC9RFujQ</a>"},{"pid":"bbd37a4edbb2cac53c10eff9849a0982b812035c","tid":2318283,"uid":134071,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"唔怪得卓悅越來越垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f53b5e9a1961d06cfa21eca42830fa299e6347","tid":2318283,"uid":54511,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"欠租了。有錢 可以創 紫黨了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a670606514b4e7ded1b1319a6c084e1b97acc137","tid":2318283,"